fixing other people that I forget that I

00:09:05.770 --> 00:09:07.330
have a problem too.

00:09:07.330 --> 00:09:09.580
And I think that’s what’s so cool about
this demonstration.

00:09:09.580 --> 00:09:13.100
Sometimes you just got to put your mask on first and get yourself sorted

00:09:13.100 --> 00:09:14.520
before you can help others.

